snippet.title: Avengers: Doomsday - Trailer 4 "The Wakandans & The Fantastic 4 Will Return" | Marvel Studios
snippet.description:
— Attention Viewers ⚠️
— This is a Fan-Made Concept Trailer for:
— Avengers: Doomsday - The Wakandans & The Fantastic 4 Will Return

— This video is a fan-made concept trailer, created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes.The goal behind this trailer is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through a concept trailer based on a unique and original idea. By combining various effects, sound design, and AI technologies, I’ve crafted a cinematic experience that reimagines familiar worlds in bold and imaginative ways. This trailer is not official and is intended to entertain, inspire, and engage with the YouTube community. Thank you for your support — now let’s dive into a world shaped by creativity and craft. 🎬✨

— In this concept trailer for Avengers: Doomsday, the story shifts toward legacy, duty, and the consequences of survival as Shuri carries the weight of a world that has taken everything from her. Having lost her family, her king, and her past, she steps fully into her role not just as Black Panther, but as a leader navigating the fragile balance between nations shaped by grief and power. Her path intersects with Talokan, where Namor stands as a reminder that kings are defined by the burdens they accept, not the battles they fight. As Wakanda looks beyond its borders, a historic meeting finally comes to pass with the Fantastic Four, signaling alliances forged across generations and timelines. The trailer positions these converging forces as essential players in the coming conflict, framing Avengers: Doomsday as a story about responsibility inherited, choices made in silence, and the fragile unity required to prevent the collapse of everything that remains.

snippet.title: VOLVÍ A FIVE NIGHTS AT FREDDY’S 4… Y LA NOCHE 6 CASI ME DA UN INFARTO 😱
snippet.description:
¡Quiubole gente enferma! el día de hoy les traigo un vídeo de FIVE NIGHTS AT FREDDY'S 4.

Volví a jugar Five Nights at Freddy’s 4 después de mucho tiempo… y NO estaba preparado para esto 😱
Este juego sigue siendo uno de los más estresantes y aterradores de toda la saga.

En este gameplay llegamos hasta la NOCHE 6, donde los animatrónicos no te dan ni un segundo de descanso. Cada sonido, cada respiración y cada puerta pueden significar tu final 💀
Aquí no hay cámaras… solo tus oídos y tus nervios.

👀 ¿Crees que FNAF 4 ya no da miedo?
Mira este video y dime si sigues pensando lo mismo…

snippet.title: Avengers: Doomsday | Full Trailer | Marvel Studios
snippet.description:
🔥 Look first! The exclusive trailer for the movie "The Avengers: Doomsday" (Avengers: Doomsday), based on the merged "Masks Off" scenario. Robert Downey Jr. returns to the MCU, but not as the hero we knew...

The multiverse is collapsing. After the cataclysmic events of the Incursions, Earth-616 faces imminent destruction. In this video, we visualize the most shocking rumors and leaks about the Fifth Phase of Marvel.:

Return of the Legend: Steve Rogers (Chris Evans) returns from the past. But this is not the Captain America that Sam Wilson remembers. The teaser shows Steve with a baby in his arms — the beginning of a new time loop that could destroy everything.

 The Fall of the Mutants: The X-Men enter their final battle. Magneto and Professor X are trying to protect the mansion from the Guardians, modified by Stark technology.

Dr. Doom without a Mask: The most anticipated moment is the meeting of Peter Parker (Tom Holland) and Victor von Doom. The mask falls off, revealing Tony Stark's face. "Stark was weak. I am necessary." Is Doom an evil version of Iron Man, or is it a violent game by Mephisto?

This concept trailer combines the storylines of "Avengers: Secret Wars", "Fantastic Four" and "Spider-Man 4" into a single epic ending to the Multiverse Saga.

🎥 CAST (Expected cast):

Robert Downey Jr. - Victor Von Doom / Doctor Doom.

Chris Evans as Steve Rogers / Nomad.

Chris Hemsworth is Thor Odinson.

Tom Holland as Peter Parker/ Spider-Man.

Hugh Jackman as Logan/ Wolverine.

Pedro Pascal — Reed Richards / Mr. Fantastic.

Benedict Cumberbatch is Doctor Strange.

I would like to clarify that this video is a concept trailer that was created purely for artistic and entertaining purposes. I have used various video editing techniques and artificial intelligence tools to bring my vision to life, and film analytics and other elements have been used to enhance the overall viewing experience. The primary goal of this trailer is to showcase my artistic vision. Thank you for your ongoing support!

The premiere of the film "Avengers: Doomsday" is scheduled for December 18, 2026

 THEORIES AND QUESTIONS: Do you think Robert Downey is playing a version of Tony Stark (Superior Iron Man) or the real Victor Von Doom, who just looks like him? Write your theory in the comments! 👇

#AvengersDoomsday #RobertDowneyJr #Marvel #Avengers #DoctorDoom  #MCU #IronMan #SpiderMan #SecretWars #ChrisEvans #Deadpool #FantasticFour #TomHolland #MarvelStudios

Y que no soy de acero
Y lo quiero
Y recordé todos los buenos momentos que viví a su lado
Cuando a mi cielo lo llenó de estrellas
Con su huella

Que fue por él todo lo que he sufrido

snippet.title: Nuestro Juramento - Julio Jaramillo (Video con Letra)
snippet.description:
🎶 Nuestro Juramento – Julio Jaramillo (Video con Letra)
Disfrutá de uno de los boleros más emblemáticos de todos los tiempos en la inconfundible voz de Julio Jaramillo, el Ruiseñor de América.
“Nuestro Juramento” es una canción cargada de amor, nostalgia y promesas eternas que marcó generaciones y sigue emocionando hasta hoy.

Este video incluye letra completa, ideal para cantar, dedicar o simplemente dejarse llevar por la magia del bolero clásico.

❤️ Un homenaje a una leyenda de la música romántica latinoamericana.


 #Jaramillo #JulioJaramillo
